quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,Sooraj ki qasam aur is ki roshni ki
  91,2,aur chaand ki jab is ke peechay niklay
  91,3,aur din ki jab ussay chamka day
  91,4,aur raat ki jab ussay chhupa le
  91,5,aur aasman ki aur is zaat ki jis ne usay banaya
  91,6,aur zameen ki aur is ki jis ne usay phelaya
  91,7,aur ensaan ki aur is ki jis ne is ( ke aaza ) ko barabarkiya
  91,8,phir is ko badkaari ( se bachney ) aur parhaiz gari karne ki samajh di
  91,9,ke jis ne ( apne ) nafs ( yani rooh ) ko pak rakha woh morad ko pouncha
  91,10,aur jis ne usay khaak mein milaya woh khasaray mein raha
  91,11,( qoum ) smod ne apni sar kashi ke sabab ( paighambar ko ) jhatlaya
  91,12,jab un mein se aik nihayat badbakht utha
  91,13,to khuda ke paighambar ( Saleh ) ne un se kaha ke khuda ki oontni aur is ke pani peenay ki baari se izr karo
  91,14,magar unhon ne paighambar ko jhatlaya aur oontni ki koncheen kaat den to khuda ne un ke gunah ke sabab un par azaab nazilkiya aur sab ko ( halaak kar ke ) barabar kar diya
  91,15,aur is ko un ke badla lainay ka kuch bhi dar nahi
  92,1,raat ki qasam jab ( din ko ) chupale
  92,2,aur din ki qasam jab chamak utthay
  92,3,aur is ( zaat ) ki qasam jis ne nar aur madah peda kiye
  92,4,ke tum logon ki koshshn terhan terhan ki hai
  92,5,to jis ne ( khuda ke raste mein maal ) diya aur parhaiz gari ki
  92,6,aur naik baat ko sach jana
  92,7,is ko hum aasaan tareeqay ki tofeq den ge
  92,8,aur jis ne bukhalkiya aur be parwa bana raha
  92,9,aur naik baat ko jhoot samgha
  92,10,usay sakhti mein p_hnchayin ge
  92,11,aur jab woh ( dozakh ke garhay mein ) giray ga to is ka maal is ke kuch kaam nah aeye ga
  92,12,hamein to raah dikha dena hai
  92,13,aur akhirat o radnia hamari hi cheeze hain
  92,14,so mein ne tum ko bharakti aag se mutnabba kar diya
